Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）蒙武(もうぶ)たちからの連絡が\N途絶えたことを懸念した王騎(おうき)は―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:06.80,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Worried over his loss of communication with Meng Wu's group,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:12.61,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Wang Qi hurried forward with his subordinate troops and finally captured the enemy's headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:12.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,配下の兵を急がせて 進軍し\Nついに 自ら 敵の本陣を捕らえた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが そこには\N蒙武たちの姿も 敵の影もなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:19.49,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,But there was no sign of Meng Wu's group nor the enemy whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:27.76,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Meng Wu's group that had followed Pang Nuan into the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:27.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのころ 龐煖(ほうけん)を追って\N山中に入った蒙武たちは―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:31.78,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,was put in desperate straits when they were met with an enemy ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:32.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伏兵の攻撃を受けて\N窮地に陥っていたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:36.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣を捨てた趙(ちょう)軍が\N蒙武たちに―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:40.27,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Wang Qi, aware that the Zhao Army had abandoned their headquarters in order to try to finish off Meng Wu's group,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:40.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とどめを刺そうとしていることを\N察知した王騎は―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:43.10,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,immediately followed after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:43.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直ちに あとを追った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:58.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが この危急のときにも\N王騎は ある違和感を覚えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:58.55,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,But despite what a critical situation it was, Wang Qi had a certain feeling of discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:02.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）やはり\Nかすかに策略の気配を感じます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.87,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,I do indeed faintly sense a plan. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:09.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 現在の趙軍の配置と\Nその戦い方から考えると―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:10.06,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,But if I consider the Zhao Army's current position and method of fighting, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:14.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状況から 大規模な展開を\Nすることは ありえません
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:13.86,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,there is no way for this situation to develop into anything on a large scale. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:19.39,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,Even so, if it poses a threat to me... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも なお\N私を脅かすとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:24.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張り巡らされた策略は\N恐ろしく深い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:24.51,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,the strategy they've laid out is phenomenally deep. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）時は紀元前 春秋戦国時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:29.24,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The setting is before the common era, in the Spring and Autumn Warring States Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:33.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名もなき存在から\N百人隊の将にまでなった少年 信(しん)は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:33.22,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Xin, the boy that came from obscurity to become the general of a Hundred-Man Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:38.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,激戦の真っただ中で活躍を続け\N秦国軍を優勢に導いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:38.51,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,continued to prove himself in the height of battle and led the State of Qin Army to dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:41.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが今\Nついに姿を現した敵の総大将は―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:42.06,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But now the enemy Supreme Commander has finally shown himself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,想像を絶する存在であった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.85,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and is a being beyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:49.05,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The name of that man, whom is linked by fate to Wang Qi, is Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:48.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎との因縁を持つという\Nその男の名は“龐煖”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:52.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦局は いよいよ 大きく動きだす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:53.38,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The state of the war has finally started to really shake up.
