Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:28.35,Kingdom-Title-Op,Title,0,0,0,,Central Performers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:36.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政(せい)）俺に伝えねばならぬこととは\N何だ？ 楊端和(ようたんわ)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:36.11,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,What is the thing that you must tell me, Yang Duan He?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）政…\Nお前の弟 成蟜(せいきょう)の反乱を共に戦い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:44.58,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Zheng, it has been approximately one year since I fought alongside with you to quell your brother Chengjiao's rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎮めてから約１年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:48.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らは山の世界に戻り\N戦に明け暮れた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:48.12,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,We have returned to the Mountain World and have spent all our time fighting wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:52.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）その結果\N我が勢力は かつてなく強大になり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:52.98,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,The result of those wars is that my power is greater than it has ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その及ぶ範囲は 北の騎馬民族と\Nぶつかる所まで広がった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:58.09,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,And the range of that power has expanded to collide with the Northern equestrian tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北の騎馬民族…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.38,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Northern equestrian tribe? The Xiongnu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:03.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,匈奴(きょうど)か\N（楊端和）そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:02.77,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,匈奴たち 北の騎馬民族は―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:15.81,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,The Xiongnu, the Northern equestrian tribe, are a far greater enemy than any Mountain People tribe we have fought in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで戦ってきた山の民とは\Nワケが違う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:23.98,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Their high level of fighting ability, their deep understanding of the art of war, the large scale of their army...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）\N彼らは その戦闘能力の高さ―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:23.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦術に対する理解の深さ\N軍の規模の大きさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.71,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Whichever you pick, they are an incomparably stronger fighting tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:27.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どれを取ってもケタ違いの\N戦闘民族だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.21,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,承知している
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:35.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから ヤツらの勢力範囲に\N国境を接している秦(しん) 趙 燕(えん)の各国は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:32.71,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,That is why the states that border their sphere of influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.62,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Qin, Zhao, and Yan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:39.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに延々と続く城を築いて\N防衛に努めている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:39.80,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,are endlessly building castles in an attempt to form a defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その匈奴を討つべく―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.27,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,In an attempt to defeat those Xiongnu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らは総力８万の軍を挙げて\N彼らの地に攻め入った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:46.30,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,we raised an army totaling 80,000 soldiers and invaded their land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.12,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,But you are here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが お前たちは 今ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.51,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Does that mean you defeated the Xiongnu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ということは\N匈奴を討ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… いや 討てなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.46,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,No, we could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:01.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君(しょうぶんくん)）討てなかったとは？\Nでは 敗れたと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.92,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,You couldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.55,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Then are you saying you were defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗れたわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:03.11,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Nor were we defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:07.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,匈奴軍の主力が\N集まっているという地へ赴いたが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:07.86,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,We moved our troops to the place that was said to be where the Xiongnu Army's main force was gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.62,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,but there was no enemy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵がいなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.58,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,There was no... enemy there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵がいなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:17.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我らは そこで恐ろしいものを見た\Nそれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.19,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,We saw a dreadful sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:17.83,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:24.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）\N10万をはるかに超える匈奴の屍(しかばね)だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:24.47,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Xiongnu corpses numbering far over 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:28.23,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Over 100,000... corpses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10万を超える屍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そなたたち山の民が着く前に\N何者かが匈奴を討ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:34.48,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,So before you Mountain People had arrived, they had been killed by someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 何者が… ほかの騎馬民族か？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:38.62,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,But who? Another equestrian tribe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:42.24,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H68609E&\bord3\fs60\pos(640,201)\frx7}Northern Equestrian Tribe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）\Nひと口に“北の騎馬民族”というが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.24,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,We call them the Northern equestrian tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際には 月氏(げつし) 東胡(とうこ) 匈奴など―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:48.10,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,But I have heard there are actually several tribes called Yuezhi, Donghu, Xiongnu and others that are struggling for supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:44.94,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H5A7DB0&\bord3\fs50\pos(640,231)}Yuezhi {Orange}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:44.94,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7A9B8C&\bord3\fs50\pos(1116,495)}Donghu {Green}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:44.94,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H685F9D&\bord3\fs50\pos(192,535)}Xiongnu {Red}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:48.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さまざまな民族が\N覇権を争っていると聞く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:53.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）初めは 私も そう思った\Nしかし 違ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.52,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,At first, I thought so as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.18,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,but that was incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.43,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,What defeated over 100,000 Xiongnu was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10万を超える匈奴を討ったのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.50,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,the Zhao Army forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙の軍勢だった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ…\N（昌文君）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.75,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.09,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H685F9D&\bord3\fs50\frx34\fry346\pos(650,151)}Xiongnu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.09,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H505A86&\bord3\fs50\frx26\fry350\pos(584,593)}Zhao
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）\N我らが匈奴の屍を見たのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.93,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,The place we saw the Xiongnu corpses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:11.85,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,was nearby a strategic cornerstone protecting the Northern Zhao border, a castle called Yanmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:11.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙の北の国境を守る軍事上の要\N雁門(がんもん)という城の近く
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.64,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,500)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H4F5A86&\bord3\fs50\frx42\fry10\frz359.1\pos(1158,481)}Yanmen {Right}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:17.73,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,1000)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H4E5A85&\bord3\fs50\pos(1076,429)}Yanmen {Right}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:17.73,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,1000)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H69619E&\bord3\fs50\pos(234,195)}Xiongnu {Top}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:17.73,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,1000)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H505A86&\bord3\fs50\pos(230,610)}Zhao {Bottom}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.79,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,In other words, the Zhao Army forces that had been sent northward
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:17.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 北に派遣された趙の軍勢が\N匈奴の地に攻め入り 打ちのめした
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:17.24,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,invaded Xiongnu land and defeated them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.58,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,That is what I am saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ということだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（机をたたく音）\Nありえぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:21.74,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:26.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は 趙の都 邯鄲(かんたん)に\N多くの諜報員を送り込んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.78,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,We have many intelligence operatives sent into Zhao's capital, Handan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）たとえ北の端でも\N趙が10万もの大軍と戦を行ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:32.19,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Even if it was at their northern tip, if Zhao sent enough of an army to fight a war against 100,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この咸陽(かんよう)にも知らせが入るはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.79,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,then we would be aware of it here in Xianyang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:40.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろうな\Nだが お前たちは現に知らなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:40.47,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Indeed... but the fact is that you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしいことだと思わぬか？ 政
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:43.25,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Don't you think that is a frightening revelation, Zheng?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）\Nなぜ お前たちは知らぬと思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.52,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Why do you think you did not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙が情報を封鎖しているからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.30,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Because Zhao has a blockade on information getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のために？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.56,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）北に 匈奴を討つほどの\N強力な軍がいることを隠すため
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:56.93,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,In order to hide the fact that they have an army strong enough to defeat the Xiongnu at the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠して どうする？\N（政）隠して…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.93,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,And by hiding it, what will they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.57,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,By hiding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.19,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,What will they do, knowing that fact is hidden, Zheng?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠しておいて どうする？ 政
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.04,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,With it hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）隠しておいて…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:21.12,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,800)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H4E5A85&\bord3\fs40\pos(936,126)}Yanmen {Top}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:16.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）今 展開されている\N秦 趙 両国の戦に参入させる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:16.98,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,They'll introduce it into the war going on between Qin and Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:22.24,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,If the Qin and Zhao armies are currently struggling for supremacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）もし今 秦 趙 両軍の\N力が拮抗(きっこう)しているとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.00,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,0)\c&H1C1E2B&\3c&HCCDBEA&\bord3\fs50\pos(264,552)}Qin {Left}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.00,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,1000)\c&H1C1E2B&\3c&HCCDBEA&\bord3\fs50\pos(774,552)}Zhao {Right}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.75,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\c&H1C1E2B&\3c&HCCDBEA&\bord3\fs50\move(264,552,386,508)}Qin {Left}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.75,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\c&H1C1E2B&\3c&HCCDBEA&\bord3\fs50\move(774,552,880,510,0,3234)}Zhao {Right}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:26.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この新たな軍の出現で\N戦は一気に決着がつくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:26.61,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,with the appearance of this new army, the war will be settled instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:28.63,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,2000)\c&H1C1E2B&\3c&HCCDBEA&\bord3\fs50\pos(386,508)}Qin {Left}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:30.42,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\c&H1C1E2B&\3c&HCCDBEA&\bord3\fs50\pos(880,510)}Zhao {Right}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 その結果は…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.04,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,And of course, the result will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（机をたたく音）\Nそんなバカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.68,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:37.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）\Nその軍が南に向かうというのは\Nあくまで推測だが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:37.64,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,The idea that that army will travel South is nothing but a prediction,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし事実だとしたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.60,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,but if it turns out to be the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを考え 実行している者は\N恐ろしい策略家だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:44.69,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,the one who thought of that plan and enacted it is a fearsome strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:49.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）そして\N趙軍を指揮して 匈奴を討った男も
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:49.21,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,And he is also the man that directed the Zhao Army and defeated the Xiongnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:55.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき\N匈奴の屍を見て驚いたのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:59.24,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,When we first discovered them, we were most surprised not by the number of the dead, but how they were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数の多さではなく 殺され方だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:03.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抵抗した形跡もなく\N一方的に殺されていた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:03.97,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,There was no sign of resistance, they were killed overwhelmingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:08.72,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Their defeat was not the result of "military force", it was the result of "strategy".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは武の力ではなく\N策略によって敗れた結果だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.02,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Do you think it's the work of the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:14.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ人物の仕業か？\N（楊端和）十分 考えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.39,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,It is well within reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:18.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僅かに生き残った戦士から\N聞き出した その男の名は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:18.35,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,I heard the from the few that did survive, that man's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.18,Kingdom-Main,Yang,0,0,0,,Li Mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楊端和）“李牧(りぼく)”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）来ましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.49,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Looks like they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂(てん)）ハッ… 何だ？ この音\N（蒙毅(もうき)）まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.60,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,What's this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.24,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:49.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）あれは… 趙の騎馬隊だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.30,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.03,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,a Zhao mounted unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ こんな所に？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.86,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Why are they at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:06.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏加(ぎか)）\Nお迎えに上がりました 李牧さま
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:06.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We're here to pick you up, Lord Li Mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:12.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あれは…\N（李牧）魏加どの ご苦労さまです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.53,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.69,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Good work, Lord Wei Jia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.71,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,You deceived us, Kaine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダマしたのか？ カイネ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:30.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構いいヤツだと思ってたのに\N敵だったなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:30.24,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I thought you were a pretty good person, but you were an enemy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイネ）\N子供のケンカみたいなこと言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.08,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Don't talk like this is some kid's spit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.64,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,What is happening on this land right now is a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 この地で\N行われているのは戦だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺すのか？ 僕たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.97,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:50.83,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Rest easy. Lord Li Mu will not murder people who are not directly related to the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:50.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李牧さまは 戦に 直接\N関わりのない者を殺(あや)めたりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦が終わりしだい\Nお前たちは解放される
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.98,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,You two will be released when the war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイネ）\Nじゃあな 河了貂(かりょうてん)　ここでお別れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.17,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,See ya, He Liao Diao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.49,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.68,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,If you really do become a strategist,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:03.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が本当に軍師なったら\Nまた どこかの戦場で会うかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.41,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,perhaps we'll meet again on a battlefield somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん 敵として\N（貂）クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.50,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Of course, that would be as enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:12.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ それと お前がくれた食べ物\Nおいしかったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:12.42,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Oh, and the food you gave me was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）待て！\N（カイネ）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.11,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.95,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Please just tell me one thing, Kaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつだけ教えてくれ カイネ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:20.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李牧とは何者なんだ？\Nこの戦と どう関わっている？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.82,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Who is Li Mu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.60,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,How is he connected to this war?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,質問が２つだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.88,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,That was two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう　１つ目だけ教えてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.40,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll just answer the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:31.02,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Do you know of people called Zhao's Three Divas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙の“三大天”というものを\N知っているか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.27,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Of course I know of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:36.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん知っている\N藺相如(りんしょうじょ)　趙奢(ちょうしゃ)　廉頗(れんぱ)…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.63,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Lin Xiangru, Zhao She, and Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:42.00,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,They were great heroes that once fought fierce battles against the State of Qin's Six Great Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて我が秦国の六大将軍とも\N激しく戦った偉大な英雄たちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:46.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）だが\N藺相如も趙奢も 既に この世になく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:46.49,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,But Lin Xiangru and Zhao She have already departed from this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗は魏に亡命して\Nもはや三大天など存在しないはず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:50.58,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,And Lian Po fled to Wei. The "Three Great Divas" should no longer exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ そんな過去の話を…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.28,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,Why would you bring up a story of such long past?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:59.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに\Nかつての三大天は もういない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:59.27,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,It's true that the former Three Great Divas are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:03.49,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,But what if a new Three Great Divas were being born...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:03.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 新たな三大天が\N生まれつつあるとしたら？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 李牧が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.79,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:06.73,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Li Mu is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.61,Kingdom-Main,Kaine,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:23.91,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,667)\fs50\fade(0,800)}State of Zhao Three Great Divas{\fs60}   Li Mu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:28.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）趙軍本陣が\N置かれていた所から 南東の方角に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:28.45,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Southeast from where the Zhao Army headquarters was left
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.48,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,there was an area with odd terrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わった地形の場所があった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:35.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大きく開けた平地を\N切り立った断崖が 三方から―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:35.50,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,A large open flatland with sheer cliffs on three sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:38.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釣り鐘のような形に\N囲っているのである
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.23,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,creating a bell-shaped enclosure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その中で 断崖の麓に追い込まれ\N包囲を受けている軍があった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:43.81,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Inside it was an army that had been chased to the foot of a cliff and surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:50.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,包囲しているのは\N趙軍の中核を成す趙荘(ちょうそう)軍１万2,000
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:50.01,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The side doing the encircling was the Zhao Zhuang Army of 12,000, which made up the core of the Zhao Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 その本陣には趙荘と…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:54.61,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Of course, in the headquarters of that army was Zhao Zhuang and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖がいた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.94,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:01.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一方 包囲されているのは\N蒙武 隆国(りゅうこく)軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:01.38,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And the ones that were being surrounded were the Meng Wu and Long Guo Armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:05.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに至るまでに 分断され\N攻撃され続けた彼らは―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:05.64,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,After being were continuously divided until they were brought here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,既に1,000騎未満
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.66,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,they now only have 1,000 mounted soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:12.41,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And of those remaining, they are all wounded and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:12.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残った者も\N全員が傷つき 疲れ切っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隆国）活路が見いだせぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.44,Kingdom-Thought,Long,0,0,0,,I don't see any means of escape. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.67,Kingdom-Thought,Long,0,0,0,,Behind us is a sheer cliff which we cannot escape up. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,背後は断崖で 逃げ道はなく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵を突破しようにも―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:22.93,Kingdom-Thought,Long,0,0,0,,And as for trying to break through the enemy, not only are the soldiers exhausted, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:26.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵たちには もちろん\N蒙武にさえ力が残っておらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.35,Kingdom-Thought,Long,0,0,0,,but even Meng Wu has no strength left. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや これまでか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.56,Kingdom-Thought,Long,0,0,0,,Is this... as far as we go?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.04,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:46.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）来ましたぞ 龐煖さま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:46.45,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,He's here... Lord Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:07.34,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It has been 5 days since the war between the States of Qin and Zhao began.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:07.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N秦 趙 両国の戦が始まって５日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:11.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに 両軍の大将同士が対峙(たいじ)した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:11.37,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now finally, the Great Generals of the two armies have confronted each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:27.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）ここに至るまでに\N随分 時間が かかりましたね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:27.30,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,It sure took quite a while for us to reach this point, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:30.64,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Liao...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:58.27,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,You've gotten tired of waiting as well, haven't you, Pang Nuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:58.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）あなたも\N待ちわびたでしょう？ 龐煖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:02.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５日… いや ９年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.18,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,5 days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.60,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:02.40,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,9 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:08.18,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Now, shall we settle this once and for all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）\N決着をつけるとしましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.42,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,The time has finally come, hasn't it, Lord Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）いよいよですね 信どの\N（信）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:23.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大天旗を掲げよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.63,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Raise the Great Diva Flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.47,Kingdom-TL Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,Flag: Great Diva
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いきなり何だ？ あいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're those guys doing all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:42.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪(はいろう)）あの旗は大天旗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.36,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,That flag... It's the Great Diva Flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）あそこに\N趙の三大天がいるってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.98,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Does that mean that one of Zhao's Three Great Divas are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:54.49,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\fs40\pos(640,663)}State of Zhao Three Great Divas {\fs60}  Pang Nuan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.53,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Even if he's just offhandedly been called one of the Three Great Divas,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騰(とう)）にわか三大天でも\Nその名の効果はあるようですね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.54,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,that title does seem to have an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフッ… 当然でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.50,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“三大天”の名は\N人々の心に刻まれているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:06.51,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,The title of Three Great Divas is etched into people's hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:14.05,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,along with the vibrant battle history of those three being on-par us Six Great Generals of the State of Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:10.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たち秦国の六大将軍とも\N互角に渡り合った―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの３人の輝かしい戦歴と共にね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:18.07,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,With the memories that the waving of that Great Diva Flag calls back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）\Nその記憶を呼び覚ます大天旗が\N翻れば 士気は跳ね上がりますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.00,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,morale is sure to shoot up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:25.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では こちらも\N六大将軍の旗“六将旗”を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:25.84,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Then we should raise the flag of the Six Great Generals, the "Six Generals Flag".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:30.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）そんな物は\Nありませんよ 騰 ココココッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:28.06,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,There is no such thing, Teng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.40,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,This really takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:35.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,懐かしいですねえ\Nあの旗を掲げた軍と戦うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.03,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Fighting an army that has raised that flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:37.96,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,While we're being nostalgic..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:41.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,懐かしいついでです\N久々にアレをやっておきましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:41.04,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,why don't we do {\i1}that{\i0} for the first time in quite a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.04,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This kinda... looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:45.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）なんか やべえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:50.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全に けおされちまってる\Nなんとかして こっちの勢いを…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,They're completely overwhelmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We need to do something and add out power to them or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're these cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:57.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ この声は\Nこっちの陣地から聞こえてくるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.06,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,They're coming from our position!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:43.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフフッ…\N久々に聞きましたよ この声を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.74,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,It's my first time hearing it in quite a while, these cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:44.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ～て…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.35,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは 早速 始めましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:48.37,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Shall we now get this started?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）\Nこたびの趙との戦には 謎があった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:58.46,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,There's a mystery to this war with Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三大天亡きあとの趙にあって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:07.17,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,With the Three Great Divas dead, who was it in Zhao that led an army in an attack on our State of Qin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:07.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大軍を率いて 我が秦国に\N攻め入ってきたのは何者なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:13.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やがて伝わってきた\N趙軍 総大将の名は龐煖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:12.79,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,We eventually were told that the Zhao Supreme Commander's name is Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:18.02,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,But according to what you told me, that Pang Nuan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが その龐煖は\Nお前が語っていたとおり―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:23.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“純粋な武の結晶”であり\N人を率いるたぐいの者ではなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:23.02,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,is a pure manifestation of war. Not the kind of person who can lead other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:29.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのような男に 一国の\N軍の総大将が務まるとは思えぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:28.89,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,I do not think such a person would be appointed as Supreme Commander for a whole kingdom's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし 楊端和が\N知らせてくれた李牧という男が―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:36.73,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,But if this Li Mu man that Yang Duan He informed me of is manipulating the army from the shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,影で軍を動かしているとすれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.48,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Then the mystery is solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）謎は解けますな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:44.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが もし そうだとすると…\N（昌文君）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.66,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,But... If that is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:48.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）李牧 尋常な男ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.00,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Li Mu is not an ordinary man. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10万を超える匈奴を\N討ち果たす力を持ちながら―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.54,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,While he has the power to slay a Xiongnu army of over 100,000, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:56.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姿を隠して 秦軍に襲いかかる時を\N見計らっている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:56.30,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,he is hiding himself and looking for an opportune time to attack the Qin Army. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.85,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Why is he going so far to setup a strategy? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:00.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ そこまで策略を弄する？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李牧のねらいは 一体 何なのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.49,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Just what in the world is Li Mu's goal? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:11.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では まずは こちらに\Nお相手願いましょうか 趙荘さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:11.56,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Now then, would you mind taking me as your opponent, Mr. Zhao Zhuang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（士官）\N騎馬隊 出陣！ 騰副官に続け！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Mounted unit, depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Follow Aide Teng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Wang Qi Army's mounted unit is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）\N王騎軍の騎馬隊 来ます！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.38,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Archers, take your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弓兵 構えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長１）弓兵 構えい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.33,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Archers, take positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.17,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長１）射(う)て！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:37.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右へ かわす\N（士官）右方旋回！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.69,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Dodge to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:36.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Turn to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:47.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長１）左に向かったぞ！\Nそちらでも矢を放て！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.73,Kingdom-Main,Zhao Guy,0,0,0,,They're heading left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.98,Kingdom-Main,Zhao Guy,0,0,0,,Fire your arrows that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長２）\N間に合わぬ！ 懐に入られた！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.77,Kingdom-Main,Zhao Guy,0,0,0,,They won't make it in time! They're right in our bosom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長２）歩兵 構えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.61,Kingdom-Main,Zhao Guy,0,0,0,,Foot soldiers, take positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入った！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:00.83,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,They're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nけど とんでもなく それた所に\N入っちまったぞ あの副官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But that aide got led really astray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.69,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:11.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）\Nフフフッ… あれでいいんですよ\N騰の狙いどおりです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.31,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,That's exactly what Teng was aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:19.44,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Now then! Next is time for you foot soldiers to take the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:20.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）さあ！ 次は\Nあなたたち歩兵の出番ですよ 童 信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:24.39,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Youngster Xin, I have a big job waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:25.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大仕事が待っています\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Zhao Zhuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）趙荘さま！\N左の軍より 救援の要請です！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There is a call for reinforcements from the left army!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:36.82,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We cannot stop the momentum of the Wang Qi Army's mounted unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突入した王騎軍 騎馬隊の\N勢いが止まりません！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.92,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Do not panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慌てるな　横に敷いた陣は\N貫かれることを防ぐのが定石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:41.41,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,A horizontally arranged formation will always block against penetration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）横の部隊を\N敵前方に回して補強せよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.80,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Side unit, move in front of the enemy and reinforce the defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（士官）騰副官！\N奥に厚みを作られました！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:49.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Aide Teng! They've created a dense formation further in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:55.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騰）横に展開する\N敵の弓兵を始末するぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.36,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Spread out horizontally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.44,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,We are going to deal with the enemy's archers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）頼みましたよ\N（信たち）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.84,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.55,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,all of you foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歩兵の皆さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）全軍 突撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.55,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,All units, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突撃だー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:16.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Zhao Zhuang! Foot soldiers from the formation on Wang Qi's right side are advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:16.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）\N趙荘さま！ 王騎軍の右側の陣から\N歩兵が前進してきます
