Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.29,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,That Wang Qi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）王騎め…\N我が軍の左側が―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:23.58,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,He saw through to the fact that the left side of our army is the cornerstone of our defense and attacked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:23.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守備の要であることを\N見抜いて 攻めてきたか
