Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:27.47,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,He's planning to first take away this headquarters' shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:31.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 先ほどの騎馬隊で\N楔(くさび)を打ったつもりならば―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:31.14,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,But if he intended to drive a wedge in with that mounted unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えが甘いぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.38,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,then he's too optimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:38.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左の全軍 防御体勢！\N１歩も下がらず 敵を跳ね返せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:36.00,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,All left units, defensive positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.71,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Without retreating one step, deflect the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:45.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長２）来るぞ！ 前の歩兵は\N密集して 敵の突撃に備えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.30,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:45.22,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Front foot soldiers, crowd together and prepare for the enemy's charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.80,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Rear archers, ready your bows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:48.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長２）\N後ろの弓兵は弓を構えい！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.97,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Arrows are gonna be coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ矢が来るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.46,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部隊長２）射て！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.52,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Now, Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今だ！ 飛信(ひしん)隊 左に旋回だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.25,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Turn to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:01.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）足を止めるな！ 走れ 走れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't stop for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.24,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）あの歩兵たち\N本陣に向かってくるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.93,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Those foot soldiers... they're heading towards the headquarters!
