Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:12.25,Kingdom-Map,Signs,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H4D5984&\bord3\pos(1100,615)}Right Army {Right piece}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:12.15,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,So Wang Qi's goal was the headquarters from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）\N王騎のねらいは\N最初から この本陣か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 敵に横を見せれば\N格好の矢の的だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:16.06,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,But showing your side to your enemy makes you quite a target for arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:21.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢が少ないぞ\N左の軍の弓兵は何をしているのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There are so few arrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:21.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What are the left army's archers doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.82,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me, Wang Qi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）\Nバカにしているのか？ 王騎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.61,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,If you could just suddenly attack the headquarters from the start and be successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:34.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いきなり本陣を攻めて成功するなら\N誰でも そうする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:34.28,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,then anyone would do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが難しいから\N周囲から攻めていくのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:38.07,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,It is because that it's difficult that you start your attack from the surrounding armies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:42.07,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,He may be trying to catch us off guard by attacking the headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に 虚をついて\N本陣を狙ったつもりかもしれぬが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.33,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,but with the speed of foot soldiers, that surprise attack will not get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歩兵の足で その奇襲は通用せぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:51.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）左の軍は守備の要… だが\N待ち受けるだけが守備ではないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.74,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,The left army is the cornerstone of our defense
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.41,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,but simply lying in wait is not defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:57.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歩兵隊 突撃！\N王騎軍 歩兵隊の横腹を食い破れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.61,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Foot soldier unit, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:57.79,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Bite through the side of the Wang Qi Army's foot soldier unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:06.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！ 敵の歩兵隊を分断したぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:06.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Good! We've divided the enemy foot soldier unit apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:11.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）信どの！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:10.95,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:14.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵が動いてきましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.45,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,The enemy has moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！\N全部 王騎将軍の作戦どおりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:15.05,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's all going according to General Wang Qi's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:22.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）大仕事？\N（王騎）陽動です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:20.72,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Big job?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:22.32,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,A diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.95,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,Perhaps the word "decoy" would be more easy to understand here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この場合 囮(おとり)と言ったほうが\N分かりやすいでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:31.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）敵の陣形を崩すのに\N最も手早い方法は―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:31.92,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,The quickest way to destroy an enemy's formation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:34.50,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,is to have the enemy move for you on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:34.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵に自ら動いてもらうことです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:39.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちに囮になって\N敵をおびき出せってことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:39.49,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,So you want us to be decoys and lure out the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:43.39,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,I think quite a bit of blood will be spilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多くの血を\N流すことになると思いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:46.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでなくては\N相手も出てきません
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:46.28,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,but unless we do, the enemy will not budge either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:49.03,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,A lot of blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:52.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）多くの血… 今更\N血を流すことを恐れたりはしねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:52.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of shedding blood now after all we've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.61,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,but if all of us foot soldiers become decoys
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち歩兵が全員 囮になって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 誰が\N実際に敵の本陣を攻撃するんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:57.82,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,who exactly is actually going to attack the enemy headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:02.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）フフフフッ…\N決まっているでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.26,Kingdom-Flashback,Wang,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
